{This natural recapture seems to be the best move.} 8. exd5 $1 Re8+ 9. Be2 Bg4 
{White's Bishop is under dire pressure, but if he plays f3 to ease it he will 
find that he has difficulty castling because of the open diagonal from a7 to 
g1.} *

