11. Kf1 $1 {Moving the King like this lets Black show off his active pieces by 
sacrificing the Rook in order to net White's Queen.} Nxd4 12. Bxa8 $1 {If White 
cannot get away with this piece snatch -- and he cannot -- then his entire plan 
with Kf1 is bankrupt.} Ba6+ {The point. White's King gets semi-trapped behind 
his own lines, and Black's minor pieces swoop in harrass him.} 13. Kg1 Ne2+ 
{Forcing the King into a nasty discovered check.} 14. Kf1 Nc3+ $19 {And Black 
wins the Queen.} *

